<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 William M. Hall has joined the board of directors of Liberty National Bank, 
Huntington Beach. He is chief executive of Hall &amp; Associates Inc., a real 
estate sales, development, property management and escrow company. 
</P>
</TEXT>
